How to install the mod
Make sure you are on 1.0 not 1.3 it will not work
on 𝐄𝐦𝐮𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐨𝐫 remove the update
On 𝗦𝘄𝗶𝘁𝗰𝗵 use Odyssey Downgrader https://github.com/Istador/odyssey-downgrade/releases/

